title: Nolden Named Corporation Counsel/City Attorney (City of Galesburg, IL)
text: ( Source : City of Galesburg, IL ) October 7, 2015 01:48 PM GALESBURG, ILLINOIS - The City of Galesburg is pleased to announce the appointment of Mr. Bradley A. Nolden to the position of Corporation Counsel / City Attorney , effective November 2 ,
